In its quieter moments, we see Wolverine lying in bed and hallucinating Famke Janssen in a silk negligee, which at least gives him something in common with the film’s core audience. You will of course recall, with a misty eye, that Janssen’s character, Jean Grey, was killed off in the third X-Men film in 2006, and now she is dispensing ghostly moral support.
